2023-2024 - Points

Aiden Warnholtz scores a season high 25 points for Fraport Skyliners

On May 05, 2024, Aiden Warnholtz set a season high in points in a Germany - Pro A Play-Offs game. That day he scored 25 points in Fraport Skyliners Frankfurt's road win against TBB Trier, 76-85. He also had 3 rebounds, 4 assists, 3 steals and finished the game with a 24 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Rebounds

Ifeoluwa Joshua Ajayi grabs a season high 15 rebounds for Fraport Skyliners

On May 05, 2024, Ifeoluwa Joshua Ajayi set a season high in rebounds in a Germany - Pro A Play-Offs game. That day he grabbed 15 rebounds in Fraport Skyliners Frankfurt's road loss against PS Karlsruhe LIONS, 93-79. He also had 12 points, 3 assists and finished the game with a 22 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Assists

Booker Wade Coplin dishes a season high 12 assists for Fraport Skyliners

On December 12, 2023, Booker Wade Coplin set a season high in assists in a Germany - Pro A game. That day he dished 12 assists in Fraport Skyliners Frankfurt's road win against Eisbaren Bremerhaven, 90-94. He also had 12 points, 7 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 21 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Steals

Booker Wade Coplin has a season high 5 steals for Fraport Skyliners

On January 01, 2024, Booker Wade Coplin set a season high in steals in a Germany - Pro A game. That day he reached 5 steals in Fraport Skyliners Frankfurt's road win against VfL SparkassenStars Bochum, 68-94. He also had 15 points, 4 rebounds, 5 steals and finished the game with a 24 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Blocks

Booker Wade Coplin blocks a season high 3 blocks for Fraport Skyliners Booker Wade Coplin

On April 04, 2024, Booker Wade Coplin set a season high in blocks in a Germany - Pro A game. That day he went for 3 blocks in Fraport Skyliners Frankfurt's home loss against Science City Jena, 65-77. He also had 5 points, 5 rebounds, 2 steals and finished the game with a 12 efficiency.

2023-2024 - Efficiency

Aiden Warnholtz set a season high 34 efficiency for Fraport Skyliners

On October 10, 2023, Aiden Warnholtz set a season high in efficiency in a Germany - Pro A game. That day he accomplished 34 efficiency in Fraport Skyliners Frankfurt's home win against Finke Baskets Paderborn, 95-56. He also had 24 points, 7 rebounds, 1 steal and finished the game with a 34 efficiency.
